Important filesystem directories:

/etc/cron.d - contains scheduled processes

/proc - information for all processes
/proc/$id/maps - virtual memory used by process

/var/lib/systemd/coredump/ - location of coredumps
/usr/share/applications/ - freedesktop.org application listings



Arch specific:
makepkg -sri (build + install package)
makepkg -Acs (build package tar file)
